headline: Kimberly-Clark to Announce Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2024 Results on January 28, 2025
summary: Kimberly-Clark (NYSE: KMB) will issue its fourth quarter and full year 2024 results on Tuesday, January 28. A press release and supplemental materials will be issued at approximately 6:30 a.m. EST.

headline: 3 Ultra-Reliable Dividend King Stocks That Should Increase Their Payouts to All-Time Highs in 2025, Even if There's a Stock Market Sell-Off
summary: Dividend Kings are an elite group of companies that have paid and raised their dividends for at least 50 consecutive years.  Here's why Walmart (NYSE: WMT), Colgate-Palmolive (NYSE: CL), and Kimberly-Clark (NYSE: KMB) stand out as three recession-resistant Dividend Kings poised to raise their dividends in 2025 no matter what comes.
